Package ohos.sensor.listener

Interface ISensorDataCallback<D extends SensorData<S>,S extends SensorBase>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - Indicates a sensor.
    D - Indicates sensor data.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICategoryBodyDataCallback, ICategoryEnvironmentDataCallback, ICategoryLightDataCallback, ICategoryMotionDataCallback, ICategoryOrientationDataCallback, ICategoryOtherDataCallback

    public interface ISensorDataCallback<D extends SensorData<S>,S extends SensorBase>
    A parent interface to receive sensor data.

    This interface provides methods for receiving sensor data, including the basic data and accuracy data of sensors.

    Since:
    1
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Sensors#SENSOR
